00:16:16.330 --> 00:16:18.330
Li hu t-tieni frażi favorita għalija,

00:16:18.330 --> 00:16:20.330
fil-kitba kollha ta` Alfred Kinsey.

00:16:20.330 --> 00:16:24.330
